(2510, 206, 'Change check boxes to drop down lists', 1, 102, 1, 1, '2012-01-01 20:01:45', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-01-10', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'Change the 4 check boxes under "Notification Options" to be drop down lists. The lists should have the following values:\r\n\r\nNo notification\r\nNotify for priority 1 tasks only\r\nNotify for tasks of priority 2 and higher\r\nNotify for tasks of priority 3 and higher\r\nNotify for tasks of priority 4 and higher\r\nNotify for all tasks\r\n\r\nYou will need to change the update statement to save 0, 1, 2, 3, 4 or 5 for the 6 options instead of 1 or null as it does now. You will be querying and updating the same fields that it uses now which are type tinyint.'),
