(2644, 269, 'New students are not saving - 234', 1, 102, 1, 1, '2012-01-19 23:10:24', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-01-23', '2012-01-24', 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'When you add a new student the student is not saving-and therefore not printing a label. This happens if you click the new button to add an entirely new household or if you select an adult and then try to add a new student to their family.\r\n\r\nMR: I made some changes to the stored procedures. Please test this on the QA server and see if it is working now. You will want to add a new student. Then go into the database and verify that the new student exists in the db (they should have the highest id in the people table unless someone else happens to be adding people on the QA server at the same time). The look in the weeklyattendance table to make sure that they have an attendance record.'),
