(2646, 195, 'Test Sale Editor page', 1, 109, 1, 1, '2012-01-20 00:18:43', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-02-23', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, 100, 'We need to have a page added that shows client information at the top and then lists their purchases below it. \r\n\r\nThere should be a link to this page from the testsales.php page, probably by clicking the client''s id or name.\r\n\r\nIt should be kind of laid out like this page in that there is a table at the top for the purchaser info (in the case of the example page the event) and then a list at the bottom for the different sales (in the example the event dates):\r\n\r\nhttp://216.196.242.222/facilities/website/eventpage.php\r\n\r\nWe need to have the following editing functions available:\r\n\r\n1. A button to Edit the client information\r\n2. A button next to each purchase to Edit information about the purchase\r\n3. A button to record a new purchase'),
