(2685, 269, 'New Guest not added - 252', 1, 102, 1, 1, '2012-02-02 19:24:39', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-02-06', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'Birth date is not saving correctly when adding a new guest.\r\n\r\n1. Do a name search and select an adult (age 30 or over)\r\n2. In the page to edit info add a student (the student fields should be blank except for the address if you selected an adult). Pay close attention to the age. Remember you are adding a student so put an age between 13-17.\r\n3. Save the student and check them in.\r\n4. No go to the muysql workbench and observe the birth date. Each time I did this the birth date was 1969-12-31'),
