(2707, 307, 'Validate unique email address when signing up', 1, 145, 1, 1, '2012-02-10 19:36:44', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-02-20', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'On the signup page we need to validate that the email address is unique before allowing them to move to page. You can probably do this by creating a custom validation function and writing a query that just does a count on the profile table based on the email address.\r\n\r\nWe probably also need to do this when we are creating a new profile or editing a profile within a subscription.'),
