(2788, 321, 'Empty emergency contact page', 1, 145, 1, 2, '2012-03-05 18:04:50', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-06-07', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'When we go here if the person has no contacts we are currently showing an empty page.\r\n\r\nWhat do we want to do?\r\n\r\nIf there are no emergency contacts then hide all of the tabs except the "Add" tab. Also show a message.\r\n\r\nOr maybe we want to go directly to the add form. But depending on if there are options in the add form we may need to go to the new form.'),
