(2800, 310, 'Upgrading Plan', 145, 1, 145, 1, '2012-03-07 14:59:40', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-03-07', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'After entering credit card information to update my subscription from a monthly companion to a monthly family, i was given this error:\r\n\r\nA Database Error Occurred\r\nError Number: 1318\r\n\r\nIncorrect number of arguments for PROCEDURE percnew.GetNextPaymentDate; expected 1, got 0\r\n\r\ncall GetNextPaymentDate()\r\n\r\nFilename: models/database_base.php\r\n\r\nLine Number: 152'),
(2801, 286, 'Emerg. Cont. From fellow subscription members list is not repopulating', 145, 1, NULL, 3, '2012-03-07 17:03:40', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-04-04', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'After adding someone to a profile''s emergency contacts from the subscription (the checkbox and fill in two fields). If you remove that added contact as a contact, they will not be readded to the list that first appears when selecting a new contact.\r\n\r\nMR: I am going to guess that we are running a query from on profilecontacts table and excluding an records that are found there. In this query we should probably check to see that the profilecontact record was not removed.'),
