(2817, 270, 'Student Union Label Printing - 339, 365', 1, 102, 1, 1, '2012-03-12 13:08:33', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-04-01', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'When checking in a anyone, the label prints mostly blank. The person''s name is not displayed at all, but the word "staff" was small and on the bottom of a label for a staff person.\r\n\r\nAnother reports says:\r\n\r\nWhen you print a student Label only the last name is printing and it is  printing at the very bottom of the label.'),
(2819, 141, '"label name" appears on printed labels - 357', 1, 102, 1, 1, '2012-03-12 13:12:51', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-03-14', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'Is there something we can do to remove that or is it a printer setup issue?'),
