(2835, 311, 'Show account status', 1, 145, 1, 1, '2012-03-13 15:23:50', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-03-14', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'Add a field in the Subscription box labelled "Account Status". The possible values should be active, cancelled on 00/00/0000 or expired.\r\n\r\nIf the status is not active then you should show the status as bold and red so that it jumps out at the support person.'),
