(2858, 276, 'Add password field to chcking maintenance page', 1, 104, 1, 1, '2012-04-10 02:47:20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-04-22', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'This page is accessed in vine under the setup menu.\r\n\r\nThere are 2 password fields in the checkin systems options table. We need to add the one for student union (i thiknk it is calld studentpassword) to the page. You will need to:\r\n\r\n1. Add the student union password field to the studentoptionsdesc view.\r\n2. Edit the updatestudentcheckin stored procedure to include the student union password.\r\n3. Edit the page to allow the password to be shown and edited.\r\n\r\nMake sure that when you edit the view and the procedure you get a current copy of the sql files, make the edits in the sql files, then paste it into mysql workbench. It is important to do it this way so that the sql fiels are kept up to date in svn. Make sure that you have current versions of the sql files before editing.'),
