(3053, 313, 'Card expiring notification', 1, 135, 1, 1, '2012-06-21 17:09:05', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-06-21', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'We need to have a php script that will run from time to time (probably daily) that will remind subscription owners that their payment account is expiring by sending them an email.\r\n\r\nYou can see what accounts are close to expiring by looking at the recurringpayments table for the expires field. If you join that table to the profile table you will get the list of profile members. We only want to send the email to people who have subscription rights (and who have email addresses).'),
