(3120, 308, 'Set time to gmdate', 135, 145, NULL, 2, '2012-07-18 14:02:07', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2012-07-30', NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'PHP scripts should be getting the current datetime in GMT. We don''t want to rely on the webserver''s local timezone.\r\n\r\n1. If you see any calls to time(), replace it with gmdate(''U'').\r\n2. If you see any calls to date generation functions, ensure the timezone is set to GMT/UTC.\r\n\r\nThis task does not apply to database procedures and queries using the now() function.'),
