(3262, 128, 'Google sitemap', 1, NULL, 1, 3, '2012-10-23 19:41:13', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Queued', NULL, NULL, 'create a sitemap per google instructions: https://support.google.com/webmasters/bin/answer.py?hl=en&answer=156184\r\n\r\ngoogle says it is useful if:\r\n*Your site has a large archive of content pages that are not well linked to each other, or are not linked at all.\r\n*Your site has dynamic content.\r\nBoth are true for us\r\n\r\nSitemaps are a way to tell Google about pages on your site we might not otherwise discover. In its simplest terms, a XML Sitemapusually called Sitemap, with a capital Sis a list of the pages on your website. Creating and submitting a Sitemap helps make sure that Google knows about all the pages on your site, including URLs that may not be discoverable by Google''s normal crawling process.'),
